This script will scrape all the officially listed smartphones from Samsung, LG, Apple, and Huawei on Amazon.
After gathering data through selenium and beautifulsoup, it will save the name and price in an excel spreadsheet named "results.xls"

Just run it and it will do all the work for you.
In order to run this script, you must have the following libraries installed: Beautifulsoup, selenium, webdriver_manager.chrome, xlwt, time
Furthermore, you must place the "chromedriver" file in the same directory as genericAmazonScraper.py and have google chrome installed. 

Enjoy! 

